{"id":3991,"date":"2025-06-09T10:35:14","date_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:35:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=3991"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:35:41","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:35:41","slug":"mun-mu-co-nen-nan-khong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/mun-mu-co-nen-nan-khong\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 c\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n kh\u00f4ng? H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh s\u1eb9o"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 c\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n kh\u00f4ng<\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">? <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t cho l\u00e0n da. N\u1ebfu x\u1eed l\u00fd sai c\u00e1ch, da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o v\u00e0 th\u00e2m dai d\u1eb3ng. V\u1eady khi g\u1eb7p m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7, c\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n hay kh\u00f4ng? N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n n\u1eb7n th\u00ec l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 an to\u00e0n. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang chu\u1ea9n gi\u00fap da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u v\u1ebft nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-nen-tu-nan-mun-mu-khong\"><\/span><b>C\u00f3 n\u00ean t\u1ef1 n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi l\u00e0 KH\u00d4NG n\u00ean t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7. M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh do vi khu\u1ea9n, b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1edbi da, g\u00e2y vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m. N\u1ebfu n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn vi khu\u1ea9n l\u00e2y lan, l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e2u h\u01a1n, t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 s\u1eb9o v\u00e0 th\u00e2m. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"de-gay-nhiem-trung-viem-da-nang-hon\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ec5 g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng, vi\u00eam da n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng tay ho\u1eb7c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eed tr\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn vi khu\u1ea9n t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o da. Khi\u1ebfn v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng h\u01a1n. Thay v\u00ec gi\u00fap m\u1ee5n mau l\u00e0nh, vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn v\u00f9ng da xung quanh s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf, lan r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguy-co-de-lai-seo-va-vet-tham-lau-dai\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o v\u00e0 v\u1ebft th\u00e2m l\u00e2u d\u00e0i<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec. K\u00edch th\u00edch t\u0103ng sinh s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 melanin, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m k\u00e9o d\u00e0i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ebfu t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00e2u v\u00e0o v\u00f9ng da b\u1ecb vi\u00eam, m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m kh\u00f3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3994\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3994\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3994\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-1.webp\" alt=\"Nguy c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o v\u00e0 v\u1ebft th\u00e2m l\u00e2u d\u00e0i\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3994\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Nguy c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o v\u00e0 v\u1ebft th\u00e2m l\u00e2u d\u00e0i<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-lay-lan-nhanh-chong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n l\u00e2y lan nhanh ch\u00f3ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n, d\u1ecbch m\u1ee7 v\u00e0 vi khu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lan sang v\u00f9ng da xung quanh. Khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft m\u00e0 c\u00f2n m\u1ecdc th\u00eam \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n tr\u1edf n\u00ean nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-mu-la-gi\"><\/span><b>M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u00fang v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n kh\u00e1c. M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee7 tr\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0ng b\u00ean trong. Th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u0111au khi ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3995\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3995\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3995\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-2.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3995\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00fap nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn, th\u01b0\u1eddng kho\u1ea3ng 5 \u2013 10mm.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111\u00f4i khi c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111au nh\u1ee9c.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0110\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n ch\u1ee9a m\u1ee7 tr\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0ng, d\u1ec5 v\u1ee1 khi ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> V\u00f9ng da xung quanh b\u1ecb vi\u00eam, c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u01b0ng h\u01a1n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguyen-nhan-gay-ra-mun-mu-va-nhung-yeu-to-lam-mun-nang-hon\"><\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 l\u00e0m m\u1ee5n n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh do nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c nhau, t\u1eeb vi khu\u1ea9n, b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. B\u1edfi th\u00f3i quen ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da sai s\u00e1ch. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3995\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3995\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3995\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-2.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3995\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bit-tac-lo-chan-long-do-dau-thua\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng do d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. S\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn. Khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"anh-huong-tu-my-pham-khong-phu-hop\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u1ea2nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u, paraben ho\u1eb7c c\u1ed3n kh\u00f4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da. G\u00e2y m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, vi\u1ec7c d\u00f9ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. L\u00e0m m\u1ee5n tr\u1edf n\u00ean nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"che-do-sinh-hoat-thieu-khoa-hoc\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 sinh ho\u1ea1t thi\u1ebfu khoa h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ee9c khuya, c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i l\u00e0m r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft, k\u00edch th\u00edch tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed3 \u0103n d\u1ea7u m\u1ee1, g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00eam tr\u00ean da, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u01b0ng to v\u00e0 l\u00e2u l\u00e0nh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3997\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3997\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3997\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-4.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 sinh ho\u1ea1t thi\u1ebfu khoa h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3997\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 sinh ho\u1ea1t thi\u1ebfu khoa h\u1ecdc<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"roi-loan-noi-tiet-to\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i hormone trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t, mang thai ho\u1eb7c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u1eady th\u00ec. L\u00e0m cho tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c. L\u00e0m t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cham-soc-da-sai-cach\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da sai c\u00e1ch<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y trang s\u1ea1ch, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH qu\u00e1 cao, l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ch\u1ea1m tay l\u00ean m\u1eb7t, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi khu\u1ea9n l\u00e2y lan v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u00edch m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vi-khuan-p-acnes-tan-cong-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi khu\u1ea9n P. Acnes t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi khu\u1ea9n P. Acnes sinh s\u00f4i m\u1ea1nh trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc. K\u00edch th\u00edch ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1ee5n tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf, ch\u1ee9a m\u1ee7 b\u00ean trong. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t s\u1edbm, vi khu\u1ea9n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n lan r\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3998\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3998\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3998\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-5.webp\" alt=\"Vi khu\u1ea9n P. Acnes t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3998\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Vi khu\u1ea9n P. Acnes t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng da<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-mu-phat-trien-tu-nhot-furuncles\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1eeb nh\u1ecdt (Furuncles)<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Furuncles l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00e1p-xe h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh s\u00e2u trong da do nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng nang l\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi d\u1ec5 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ecbch g\u00e2y \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khi-nao-co-the-nan-mun-mu-ma-khong-gay-hai-cho-da\"><\/span><b>Khi n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho da?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n khi n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n vi\u00eam c\u1ea5p t\u00ednh. C\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4 c\u1ed3i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u01b0ng t\u1ea5y hay \u0111au nh\u1ee9c. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00e3 gom l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u1ed5 vi\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 l\u00e2y lan vi khu\u1ea9n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da, vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt b\u1edfi c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean da li\u1ec5u ho\u1eb7c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt vi\u00ean c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. N\u1ebfu n\u1eb7n sai c\u00e1ch, da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7, v\u1ebft th\u00e2m l\u00e2u m\u1edd ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-xu-ly-khi-mun-mu-bi-vo\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn x\u1eed l\u00fd khi m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 b\u1ecb v\u1ee1<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh hay c\u1ed1 \u00fd khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 b\u1ecb v\u1ee1. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u1eed l\u00fd ngay \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 gi\u00fap da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh h\u01a1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3999\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3999\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3999\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-6.webp\" alt=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn x\u1eed l\u00fd khi m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 b\u1ecb v\u1ee1\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-6.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-6-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-6-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/34-6-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3999\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn x\u1eed l\u00fd khi m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 b\u1ecb v\u1ee1<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"rua-sach-tay-truoc-khi-cham-vao-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tay l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u vi khu\u1ea9n, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng v\u1ec7 sinh s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ee5n b\u1ecb v\u1ee1. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng. H\u00e3y r\u1eeda tay th\u1eadt k\u1ef9 b\u1eb1ng x\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng di\u1ec7t khu\u1ea9n ho\u1eb7c dung d\u1ecbch s\u00e1t tr\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n cho da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-sach-vet-thuong-va-cam-mau\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m m\u00e1u<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi m\u1ee5n v\u1ee1 ra, v\u00f9ng da xung quanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea3y m\u00e1u nh\u1eb9. H\u00e3y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00f4ng s\u1ea1ch ho\u1eb7c g\u1ea1c y t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5m m\u00e1u v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch m\u1ee7. Sau \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch v\u00f9ng da b\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1i sinh l\u00fd. Ho\u1eb7c s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, paraben hay h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"boi-kem-khang-khuan-de-giam-viem\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00f4i kem kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da, h\u00e3y thoa m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp m\u1ecfng kem kh\u00e1ng sinh, Ho\u1eb7c gel tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 Benzoyl Peroxide ho\u1eb7c Salicylic Acid, Clindamycin, Metronidazol l\u00ean v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba vi khu\u1ea9n x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp. H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0nh da. L\u01b0u \u00fd ch\u1ec9 b\u00f4i \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1ee5n, tr\u00e1nh lan r\u1ed9ng ra v\u00f9ng da l\u00e0nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"giu-am-cho-da-de-ho-tro-phuc-hoi\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1eef \u1ea9m cho da \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da kh\u00f4 h\u01a1n. V\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m. Ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, d\u1ea7u kho\u00e1ng. Ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u00e0n da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-ve-da-khoi-tac-dong-tu-moi-truong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ee5n, l\u00e0n da tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n. H\u00e3y che ch\u1eafn c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn b\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea9u trang, m\u0169 r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0nh ho\u1eb7c \u00f4 khi ra ngo\u00e0i. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF 30+ \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m v\u00e0 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3901\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3901\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3901\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6.webp\" alt=\"B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3901\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tranh-cham-tay-vao-vung-da-ton-thuong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o v\u00f9ng da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn l\u00e0 ch\u1ea1m tay l\u00ean v\u1ebft m\u1ee5n b\u1ecb v\u1ee1. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn vi khu\u1ea9n lan r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e2u l\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. H\u00e3y gi\u1eef cho v\u00f9ng da n\u00e0y s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7, v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n sai c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi khu\u1ea9n l\u00e2y lan, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7 ho\u1eb7c th\u00e2m dai d\u1eb3ng. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf da li\u1ec5u ho\u1eb7c spa uy t\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 x\u1eed l\u00fd chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 b\u1ecb v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. H\u00e3y ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1eady khi g\u1eb7p m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7, c\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n hay kh\u00f4ng? N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n n\u1eb7n th\u00ec l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 an to\u00e0n. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang chu\u1ea9n gi\u00fap da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u v\u1ebft nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4000,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3991","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3991","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3991"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3991\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4002,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3991\/revisions\/4002"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4000"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3991"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3991"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3991"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}